    {
      "id": "1448675588561698907",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2025-12-11T13:59:35.404+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Hi Andrew, atm the only output is the stitched GDS.\nPlease let me know what other data you require besides the manifest and the tile map. Both file formats are subject to change, however major changes take time, and the goal is to stitch the final reticle by end of next week.\n\nThe tile map grad is based on the smallest slot size, i.e., the quarter slot. This means that half-slot projects are two tiles large and full-slot projects are 2x2 tiles. The shuttle assignment from the [online platform](https://platform.wafer.space/shuttles/G801/assign) needs to be converted to this format.\n\nWhat output would you need for the dicing plan?",
      "author": {
        "id": "323371864074485771",
        "name": "mole99",
        "discriminator": "0000",
        "nickname": "Leo Moser (mole99)",
        "color": null,
